hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 迹的系综平均为
$$\langle \operatorname{Tr}(M^{-1})\rangle = \sum_{i=1}^N \frac{1}{\lambda_i(H)-\mu}
= -\sum_{i=1}^N \frac{1}{\mu-\lambda_i(H)}
= -N\,S(\mu)\,. $$

2. 给定条件为
$$\langle \operatorname{Tr}(M^{-1})\rangle = -\frac{2N}{5}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
-N\,S(\mu)=-\frac{2N}{5}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
S(\mu)=\frac{2}{5}\,. $$

3. 对于半径 $R=4$ 的半圆，当 $|z|>4$ 时，Stieltjes 变换为
$$S(z)=\frac{2}{R^2}\Bigl(z-\sqrt{z^2-R^2}\Bigr)
=\frac{1}{8}\bigl(z-\sqrt{z^2-16}\bigr)\,. $$

4. 令 $z=\mu$ 且 $S(\mu)=2/5$ 得到
$$\frac{1}{8}\bigl(\mu-\sqrt{\mu^2-16}\bigr)=\frac{2}{5}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\mu-\sqrt{\mu^2-16}=\frac{16}{5}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\sqrt{\mu^2-16}=\mu-\frac{16}{5}\,. $$

5. 两边平方：
$$\mu^2-16
=\mu^2-\frac{32}{5}\,\mu+\frac{256}{25}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\frac{32}{5}\mu=16+\frac{256}{25}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\frac{32}{5}\mu=\frac{400+256}{25}=\frac{656}{25}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\mu=\frac{656}{25}\cdot\frac{5}{32}=\frac{41}{10}\,. $$
